{"tid":142932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷屆孔子和平獎得獎者名單","createTime":"2017-03-04T08:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T09:36:08.000Z","uid":42188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"915ef16619a34cdb52a778ebf6172bac0e1967f4","tid":142932,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"2010年:連戰 (台灣)<br />\n得獎者拒絕領獎，主辦單位找來一名來路不明小女孩「代領」。<br />\n<br />\n2011年:普京 (俄羅斯)<br />\n得獎者拒絕領獎，俄羅斯執政黨網站還諷刺該獎「一文不值」，主辦單位安排數名俄羅斯留學生「代領」。<br />\n<br />\n2012年: 利菲南安 (加納)、袁隆平 (支那)<br />\n兩名得獎者皆沒有出席領獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2013年: 釋一誠 (支那)<br />\n唯一出席領獎的得獎者。<br />\n<br />\n2014年: 菲德爾卡斯特羅 (古巴)<br />\n獎者沒有出席領獎，主辦單位安排一名古巴留學生「代領」。<br />\n<br />\n2015年: 羅拔穆加貝 (津巴布韋)<br />\n得獎者拒絕領獎，並透過發言人斥「孔子和平獎」公信力存疑。<br />\n<br />\n2016年: 申亮亮、楊樹朋、李磊 (支那)<br />\n追贈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e7e935b29cbdb47255f35a07ded28dba6e10ba","tid":142932,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:08:45.000Z","msg":"當年係頭號大混蛋<br />\n今日化身為和平奬icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdaa2e0395fb30613471e5ce0c2323596f96b62","tid":142932,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"加埋殺過幾多人?"},{"pid":"3901136712827ac237e28ae585117bb8e9e77610","tid":142932,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加埋殺過幾多人?</blockquote><br />\n35人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f83cce09b9b2dad8f4d318e3313019ce69effb3","tid":142932,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"普京好和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji